                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-342-off1760 t18310908-342-victim2457"></join>
                     </persName>
                     
                  , from his person
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-342-person2458">
                  JAMES 
                  SHILTON
               <interp inst="t18310908-342-person2458" type="surname" value="SHILTON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-342-person2458" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-342-person2458" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I belong to a brig, which laid in Bellwharf tier. On the 30th of August I was at the Paviors' Arms public-house. I changed a sovereign, and laid out 9d.; I then had 19s. 3d., which I put into my pocket, with a medal of the late Duke of York - I saw the prisoner at the house, and gave her something to drink; I had a bad bowel complaint, and asked her to show me a bed - she took me to a house, and I laid down with my waistcoat on; I vomited, and then went to sleep - I awoke about half-past three o'clock, and found my pockets entirely emptied; I was alone in the room - I went and described her at the Police-office.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined by MR. BALL. Q. How much did you have at the house? A. A pint of beer, and half a pint of gin; I did not drink it all - I did not notice how many girls were there; I treated nobody but the prisoner - I merely went to out of the room - I did not send her out for gin, nor give her any money at all.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-342-person2459">
                  PATRICK 
                  DUFFY
               <interp inst="t18310908-342-person2459" type="surname" value="DUFFY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-342-person2459" type="given" value="PATRICK"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-342-person2459" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Policeman. On the evening of the 31st of August, I found Shilton at the door of a noted brothel, in <placeName id="t18310908-342-crimeloc1762">Isaacs-buldings, Bluegate-fields</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-342-crimeloc1762" type="placeName" value="Isaacs-buldings, Bluegate-fields"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-342-crimeloc1762" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-342-off1760 t18310908-342-crimeloc1762"></join>; in consequence of what he told me I apprehanded the prisoner, about five o'clock in the morning, at a coffee-shop; she asked me if the man had got up from the bed - I said Yes, and asked her for his money; she said she had none belonging to him; I searched her, and found 8s. and the Duke of York's medal on her - I took her to the house, and directly Shilton saw her identified her; she then said, all the money he had was 5s. 9d., and she could not have robbed him of 19s. - that he gave her the medal and 5s. 9d.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined. Q.Was he not very much intoxicated? A. Not at all; the first thing the prisoner said to me was," Is the man got out of bed."</p>
               <p>(Medal produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Priosner's Defence. What he says is false; if he changed a sovereign it was before I was in his company- when I went in he sat there drinking; he asked me and ten other females to drink - he then asked me to show him a bed, which he gave 1s. 6d. for; he gave me 5s. 9d.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18310908-342-verdict1763" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310908-342-verdict1763" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 34. - <rs id="t18310908-342-punish1764" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310908-342-punish1764" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-342-defend2455 t18310908-342-punish1764"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
